315
00:13:51,137 --> 00:13:52,657
Having said that, she still ate it.

316
00:13:52,737 --> 00:13:54,458
Just when I was pouring her water,

317
00:13:54,538 --> 00:13:56,017
I heard plates and bowls behind me

318
00:13:56,097 --> 00:13:57,098
