319
00:13:57,178 --> 00:13:58,698
Then I saw she was on the ground.

320
00:13:58,778 --> 00:14:00,137
Dad, you're a doctor.

321
00:14:00,538 --> 00:14:01,938
What happened to my mom?

322
00:14:04,977 --> 00:14:08,137
It's highly likely
that the tumor has ruptured,

323
00:14:08,578 --> 00:14:10,217
causing hemorrhagic shock.

324
00:14:10,337 --> 00:14:12,337
