328
00:14:17,257 --> 00:14:18,338
But don't worry.

329
00:14:18,418 --> 00:14:20,058
The conclusion isn't out yet.

330
00:14:20,337 --> 00:14:21,578
She's on a blood transfusion.

331
00:14:22,298 --> 00:14:23,298
Don't worry.

332
00:14:26,497 --> 00:14:27,458
Miss, what's wrong?

333
00:14:27,538 --> 00:14:28,537
Are you okay?

334
00:14:28,617 --> 00:14:29,617
I'm fine.

335
00:14:30,097 --> 00:14:30,937
Thank you.

336
00:14:31,017 --> 00:14:31,458
Sure.

337
00:14:31,538 --> 00:14:32,538
Be careful.

338
00:14:37,977 --> 00:14:38,578
Doctor,

339
00:14:38,658 --> 00:14:39,578
