340
00:14:39,658 --> 00:14:40,297
Save her.

341
00:14:40,377 --> 00:14:41,018
Calm down first.

342
00:14:41,098 --> 00:14:42,057
Calm down first, okay?

343
00:14:42,137 --> 00:14:42,858
Listen to me.

344
00:14:42,938 --> 00:14:43,458
I'm sorry.

345
00:14:43,538 --> 00:14:44,538
I'm sorry.

346
00:14:47,818 --> 00:14:49,737
