358
00:15:05,698 --> 00:15:07,497
Even if she is resuscitated,

359
00:15:07,778 --> 00:15:08,458
as you know,

360
00:15:08,538 --> 00:15:09,459
her cancer

361
00:15:09,539 --> 00:15:10,777
