461
00:19:40,619 --> 00:19:42,057
So eager to see me, did you miss me?

462
00:19:42,698 --> 00:19:43,698
Was breakfast good?

463
00:19:46,418 --> 00:19:47,418
Song Ran,

464
00:19:48,257 --> 00:19:49,098
what's the point

465
00:19:49,178 --> 00:19:50,178
