466
00:19:51,858 --> 00:19:52,498
Well,

467
00:19:52,578 --> 00:19:54,098
I find it quite meaningful.

468
00:19:55,297 --> 00:19:56,137
I'll refund you.

469
00:19:56,217 --> 00:19:57,217
Don't come again.

470
00:19:58,257 --> 00:19:59,338
I won't take a refund,

471
00:19:59,618 --> 00:20:00,698
