472
00:20:05,577 --> 00:20:06,577
Song Ran,

473
00:20:07,497 --> 00:20:09,217
I will make it clear

474
00:20:09,297 --> 00:20:10,537
with you today.

475
00:20:11,338 --> 00:20:12,338
I admit when I

476
