477
00:20:13,938 --> 00:20:14,938
I did fall for you.

478
00:20:16,017 --> 00:20:16,698
But since I knew

479
00:20:16,778 --> 00:20:17,858
you married and divorced

480
00:20:17,938 --> 00:20:18,579
during your

481
00:20:18,659 --> 00:20:19,898
three-year disappearance,

482
00:20:21,338 --> 00:20:23,258
