517
00:21:30,418 --> 00:21:30,937
Not the car.

518
00:21:31,017 --> 00:21:32,577
I don't want it. It's not worth much.

519
00:21:32,938 --> 00:21:33,778
If you can do it,

520
00:21:33,858 --> 00:21:35,977
